videos.description: Tyus Battle misses a mid-range jumper and Paschal Chukwu puts it back for an and-1 basket.
videos.headline: Chukwu scores putback for Syracuse basket

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj comes up with a block but appears to injure his left ankle on the play.
videos.headline: Dolezaj limps off court after block

videos.description: Kyle Guy shows no hesitation as he drills a 3-ball from the wing.
videos.headline: Guy hits deep 3-pointer to extend Virginia's lead
